name: JewBot9K: The Plugin based Twitch Bot
body:
## JewBot9K

This is JewBot9K, a windows forms version of all the top bots for [Twitch TV](http://twitch.tv). The plugin system is the main feature of this bot. Just add a command and everything will be taken care of.

By [JewsOfHazard](https://github.com/JewsOfHazard) and [Angablade](https://github.com/angablade).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
